    - First rest stop - mushroom paste meal, exhaustion setting in
    - Leafwhisper explaining territorial structure while Kira rests
    - Rootwalker checking pace, adjusting for Kira's limitations
    - Evening camp setup - simpler than expected, plants accommodate
